text: Jemma "Jem" Palmer (born 10 April 1986) is an English model and professional wrestler. She was briefly signed to World Wrestling Entertainment. She is also known by the name Inferno. She used this name in the 2008 British television series Gladiators. In 2011, she became known for taking part in the twelfth series of Big Brother. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Big Brother contestants Category:English professional wrestlers Category:Sportspeople from Birmingham
